extends ../layout

block append vars
  - bodyclass = 'index logo'

block content
  section
    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-md-8.col-lg-6
        .block-right-lg.block-bot-lg
          p.text-larger There is only one WGSN wordmark used across the brand and outside of it. Do not create any alternative product/brand 'logos' or variation 'logos'.
          .block-ver-md: hr
          p In the case of specific, major partnerships that may require a visual output that a ects the existing branding, Brand Design will need to be notified to study the context and brief.
          p In regards to logo requests from partners, share only the wordmark shown here.
          p The three primary colours are black, white and grey and must be used as the main option. Secondary colours can be either the Brand Blue or one of the product colours.
          p Branding is majority black and white but there does remain an option to inherit the colour of the category, product or audience if the design requires.

      .col-xs-8.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        .block-bot-lg
          include ../partials/logo

    .block-bot-lg: hr
    
    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
        h2 Downloads
        .card
          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-3
              h4 Black
              ul.list-bare
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-sm.png" download="wgsn-logo-sm.png") PNG (sm)
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-lg.png" download="wgsn-logo-lg.png") PNG (lg)
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-sm.jpg" download="wgsn-logo-sm.jpg") JPG (sm)
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-sm.jpg" download="wgsn-logo-lg.jpg") JPG (lg)
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo.svg" download="wgsn-logo.svg") SVG
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo.pdf" download="wgsn-logo.pdf") PDF
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo.eps" download="wgsn-logo.eps") EPS

            .col-xs-12.col-sm-3
              h4 White
              ul.list-bare
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-white-sm.png" download="wgsn-logo-white-sm.png") PNG (sm)
                li: a.styled(href="/downloads/wgsn-logo-white-lg.png" download="wgsn-logo-white-lg.png") PNG (lg)